### Calendar-to-SMS API Tests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or any HTTP client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1

### 1. Check SMS Service Status (requires authentication)
GET {{apiUrl}}/sms/status
Cookie: token=YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 2. Send Test SMS (requires authentication)
POST {{apiUrl}}/sms/send-test
Cookie: token=YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Check if server is running
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 4. Check API status
GET {{apiUrl}}/

### Instructions:
### 1. First log in through the frontend (http://localhost:3000)
### 2. Open browser dev tools → Application → Cookies
### 3. Find the 'token' cookie value
### 4. Replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE with the actual token value
### 5. Run the requests above
